snippet: An infant was among five people killed when a fire tore through three houses in New Jersey on Sunday, a newspaper reported, citing the county prosecutor's office....

headline.print_headline: New Jersey House Fire Kills Five, Including Infant: Report
headline.main: New Jersey House Fire Kills Five, Including Infant: Report

lead_paragraph: An infant was among five people killed when a fire tore through three houses in New Jersey on Sunday, a newspaper reported, citing the county prosecutor's office.
